snippet.title: Jötunnslayer: Hordes of Hel | Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Embark on a hazardous quest through the dark realms of Norse mythology with Hordes of Hel, a gripping roguelike horde arena survival game boasting cutting-edge graphics. Select a fallen soul condemned to suffer in Helheim and wield your blade against legions of foes in a relentless quest for redemption. In this desolate domain, divine blessings are scarce, earned only through the spilling of rivers of blood.

WISHLIST Jötunnslayer: Hordes of Hel now on Steam - https://store.steampowered.com/app/2820820/Jotunnslayer_Hordes_of_Hel/

Join our Discord - https://discord.gg/Zst6agwu8v
